title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show JULY-23-2013 TUES
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show JULY-23-2013 TUES








Prager 20130723  3 Ultimate Issues Hour: What Is a Religious Education?


Prager H3: Dennis makes the case that a religious education forces you to confront
 this essential fact:
    you are your biggest problem



Prager 20130723  2 Real IRS

Prager H2: Dennis talks to John Fund, columnist for National Review,
 about the latest developments in the IRS scandal

 Kate has a King! Dennis explains why the monarchy still means so much to so many in the UK.




Prager 20130723  1 Real Steele

Prager H1: Dennis talks to Shelby Steele about his Wall Street Journal piece
 in which he contends that the Civil Rights Establishment has begun to parody itself 
 
 Speaking of comedy, Dennis talks to comedian Yakov Smirnoff about his life in the Soviet Union
  and in the United States.
